  "title": "사슴광우병 &#39;광록병&#39; 국내 발병. 국산 녹용 안심 못해",
  "addDate": "2016. 2. 24.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220636495396",
  "html_size": 184335,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220636495396\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220636495396\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_284/isuhani_1456276956438uyBHq_JPEG/images_%281%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"194\" height=\"260\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 260px; rwidth: 194px;\" id=\"20160224_284/isuhani_1456276956438uyBHq_JPEG/images_%281%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335EF5BE24')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_284/isuhani_1456276956438uyBHq_JPEG/images_%281%29.jpg?type=w3\"></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">-이미지는 본문의 내용과 무관합니다-</span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">국내에서 사슴 광우병이라 불리는 광록병이 다시 발생하여 </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">사슴 100여마리를 매몰 처분하고 긴급 역학조사를 벌이고 있다는 기사가 나왔네요</span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">근래 국산 녹용을 이용하시는 분이 있던데, 주의하셔야 할 것 같습니다. </span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">한국은 캐나다의&nbsp;CWD(사슴만성소모성질병 - 일명 '</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">광록병')</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;감염이 된 농장에서</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">1994년 23마리</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">1997년 72마리의 엘크를 도입해서 사육을 시작했기 때문에</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">지속적으로 CWD (광록병) 이 발생하고 있다 합니다. </span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">광록병은 주로 미국, 캐나다, 한국에서 발생합니다. </span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">녹용 생산 수출을 많이 하고 있는 </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">뉴질랜드에서는 광록병에 대해 제도적으로 철저히 검수하고 있기에, 이수한의원에서는 뉴질랜드 녹용을 주로 처방합니다. </span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">국산녹용을 사용, 복용하시는 분들은 주의가 필요하겠습니다. </span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">(국산녹용은 의약품 규격한약재가</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"> 아니기 때문에 식약처의 관리, 검사가&nbsp;충분치 못합니다.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">규격한약재가 아니기에 당연히 </span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">한의원에는 공급되지 않고, 사용할 수도 없습니다)</span><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"> </span></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_129/isuhani_1456276911285j7xWM_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"269\" height=\"188\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 188px; rwidth: 269px;\" id=\"20160224_129/isuhani_1456276911285j7xWM_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335EF5BE24')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_129/isuhani_1456276911285j7xWM_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5_%281%29.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">-이미지는 본문의 내용과 무관합니다-</span>&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">-----------------기사링크 --------------------</span></p><p><br /></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"><br /></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"><font face=\"Thread-00002154-Id-0000001d\" size=\"2\"><a href=\"http://news.kbs.co.kr/news/view.do?ncd=3237279&amp;ref=A\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"con_link\">http://news.kbs.co.kr/news/view.do?ncd=3237279&amp;ref=A</a></font></span></p><div class=\"date_area\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\"></span></div><div align=\"left\" class=\"date_area\"><div class=\"og\"><div class=\"box\"><div class=\"thumb b_size\"><a href=\"http://news.kbs.co.kr:80/news/view.do?ncd=3237279\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.link','')\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><img src=\"https://dthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/?src=%22http%3A%2F%2Fnews.kbs.co.kr%2Fdata%2Fnews%2F2016%2F02%2F23%2F3237279_110.jpg%22&type=f560_336\"><span class=\"bd\"></span></a></div><div class=\"txt\"><a href=\"http://news.kbs.co.kr:80/news/view.do?ncd=3237279\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"sendClickNlog('pst.link','')\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\"><div class=\"tit\">[&#45800;&#46021;] &#49324;&#49844; &#44305;&#50864;&#48337; &lsquo;&#44305;&#47197;&#48337;&rsquo; 6&#45380; &#47564;&#50640; &#46608; &#48156;&#49373;</div><div class=\"dsc\">&lt;&#50549;&#52964; &#47704;&#53944;&gt; &#49324;&#49844; &#44305;&#50864;&#48337;&#51060;&#46972; &#48520;&#47532;&#45716; &#44305;&#47197;&#48337;&#51060; 6&#45380; &#47564;&#50640; &#44397;&#45236;&#50640;&#49436; &#45796;&#49884; &#48156;&#49373;&#54664;&#49845;&#45768;&#45796;. &#48169;&#50669; &#45817;&#44397;&#51008; &#49324;&#49844; 100&#50668; &#47560;&#47532;&#47484; &#47588;&#47792; &#52376;&#48516;&#54616;&#44256;, &#44596;&#44553; &#50669;&#54617;&#51312;...</div><div class=\"cp\">news.kbs.co.kr</div></a></div></div></div><div align=\"left\"><img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static/blog/blank.gif\" class=\"m20\" alt=\"\"></div>&nbsp;</div><div class=\"date_area\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_36/isuhani_14562769115844ACyE_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"225\" height=\"225\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 225px; rwidth: 225px;\" id=\"20160224_36/isuhani_14562769115844ACyE_JPEG/%B4%D9%BF%EE%B7%CE%B5%E5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_00000000000000335EF5BE24')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160224_36/isuhani_14562769115844A